"set colorcolumn=128

"use arrow keys to mvoe between splits works in both modes
"nnoremap <Down> <C-W><C-J>
"nnoremap <Up> <C-W><C-K>
"nnoremap <Right> <C-W><C-L>
"nnoremap <Left> <C-W><C-H>

map [1;5A <C-Up>
